description:
Polite Sleeper is a folk mess from New York City. No apologies. Since 2008 the trio earned its chameleon reputation as three sweaty troubadours hauling a stage piano and homemade trap kit around the world. This fall marks the first extended European solo tour from singer Jason Orlovich in support of the band’s latest record TURF available now. 

